/*
  4.06 Writing Text Files - Pseudocode
  1) Prompt user to enter the number of trials
  2) Check if the number of trials is at least 1000 before proceeding
  3) For each trial, generate random between 1-10 (where 10 represents your chosen
  animal)
  4) The trial ends as soon as #10 is generated.
  5) Record the number of animals observed into a text file.
  6) Repeat steps 3-5 until each trial is complete.
  7) An open text file created in Step 5
  8) Read and add the numbers in each line of the file to compute the total and average
  9) Print average results
*/
